CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 13, 1957, pg. A11 reads: "Principal Steps Down - Dr. Mason, principal of McKeesport High School, shows George Smith, president of the Student Council, the important things to be done as a high school administrator. George handled Dr. Mason's job as principal in the Turn-About Day at the school - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Principal Dr. Mason and student council president George Smith, seated behind table in McKeesport High School
